                <p xml:id="CH7x2023-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2023_CHANT_003-49a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-02-17T07:04:53.286+09:00">As for the great ru</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2023_CHANT_003-49a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-02-17T07:05:20.828+09:00">they are (defined as) the Son of Heaven, and the Three Dukes;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2023_CHANT_003-49a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-02-17T06:45:50.502+09:00">As for the minor ru these are defined as the feudal lords, the grandees, and the shi;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2023_CHANT_003-49a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-02-17T06:47:17.815+09:00">as for the commoners, these are (defined as) the craftsmen, the peasants, the merchants and the traders.</seg>
                </p>
